  "prompt": "How do I watch Formula 1 online in India?",
  "response": "In India, you can watch Formula 1 online through the following platforms:\n\n1. **F1TV Pro**: This is the official streaming service for Formula 1. F1TV Pro offers live coverage of all races, including exclusive onboard cameras, team radios, and more. You can subscribe to this service directly on the F1TV website.\n\n2. **Disney+ Hotstar**: Previously, Disney+ Hotstar had the rights to stream Formula 1 races in India. Check the platform to see if they are currently broadcasting F1, as broadcasting rights can change.\n\n3. **YouTube TV**: YouTube often streams some races online, but you may need to check to see whether they offer live coverage in your region.\n\n4. **Mobile Apps**: Depending on your mobile carrier and plan, you may have access to mobile apps that allow you to stream Formula 1 races.\n\nMake sure to check the schedules and availability, as these services may update over time.",
